{"tid":2013552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工程奪命意外 遺孀與4子女急需支援","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T15:27:18.000Z","uid":337986,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53c410804833f6964193239ba1e3e75ebe1f32de","tid":2013552,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"上月下旬一宗工業意外，無情地奪走了顏訓真的性命，後事至今仍在處理當中。現時獨力照顧4名子女的顏太直言感到徬徨，「我唔識搞（後事），交晒畀姨甥處理。𠵱家都係靠先生剩低嘅幾萬蚊積蓄，同埋親戚2、3千蚊嘅幫助，但大家都有自己嘅家庭，幫得幾耐呀。」顏太表示，自2008年結婚後，她便擔任全職家庭主婦，照顧先後出生的4名子女，以及一家人的起居飲食，而全家的開支則依靠任職地盤工人的丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解明知自己窮都生4件 講到自己養到好辛苦 咁你當初點解要生 兩個大人得個幾萬積蓄 而家冇錢養搵社會埋單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/471808/%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E9%90%B5%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-l-%E9%81%BA%E5%AD%80%E8%88%874%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-%E5%AD%96%E5%A5%B3%E5%BE%972%E6%AD%B2-%E6%9C%AA%E8%AD%98%E5%8F%AB%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F471808%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596-l-%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25AD%2580%25E8%2588%25874%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E5%25AD%2596%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25BE%25972%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%258F%25AB%25E7%2588%25B8%25E7%2588%25B8&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ea69cf58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/471808/%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E9%90%B5%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-l-%E9%81%BA%E5%AD%80%E8%88%874%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-%E5%AD%96%E5%A5%B3%E5%BE%972%E6%AD%B2-%E6%9C%AA%E8%AD%98%E5%8F%AB%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8</a>"},{"pid":"be06f184c7e64b109b3a80b131eaf508ff4945a8","tid":2013552